<L>__{interior salon, parrish townhouse night}
<A>__{after dinner, parrish, allison and susan are gathered to gether. at the bar on the other side of the room, joe watches as quince pours himself a stiff hooker of brandy.}
<C>__{joe}
<P>__{(to quince)}
<D>__{cirrhosis of the liver is the fifth leading killer of adult western males.}
<C>__{quince}
<D>__{i didn't know that.}
